\n<H3>Racing Area:</H3>	\r\nClipper Cove between Yerba Buena Island and Treasure Island.\r\n<H3>Dates:</H3>\r\nJune 17-18\r\n<H3>Schedule:</H3>	\r\n<b>Thursday, June 15</b><BR>\r\n6:00-8:00pm:&nbsp;&nbsp;Fleet Racing Tune-up-Thursday Night Series at TISC.<P>\r\n<b>Saturday, June 17</b><BR>\r\n10:00am:&nbsp;&nbsp;Report Time<BR>\r\n10:00-11:00am:&nbsp;&nbsp;Registration and Rigging<BR>\r\n11:00am:&nbsp;&nbsp;Skipper\'s Meeting<BR>\r\n12:00pm:&nbsp;&nbsp;First Race Warning Signal<BR>\r\n12:00-5:00pm:&nbsp;&nbsp;Races 1-8<BR>\r\n5:30pm:&nbsp;&nbsp;BBQ Dinner and Keg Party at TISC<P>\r\n<b>Sunday, June 18</b><BR>\r\n11:00am:&nbsp;&nbsp;Race 9 Warning Signal<BR>\r\n11:00am-4:00pm:&nbsp;&nbsp;Races 9-16<BR>\r\n4:30pm:&nbsp;&nbsp;Trophy Presentation\r\n<H3>Rules:</H3>	\r\nThe regatta will be governed by the 1997-2000 ISAF Racing Rules of Sailing, the prescriptions of US Sailing, the Vanguard 15 Class Rules, and the event sailing instructions, all of which supplement or modify the former.  The 720 degree penalty is in effect.\r\n<H3>Races:</H3>	\r\n16 Races will be attempted.  3 races constitute a series.  Competitors can discard their worst race if 8 races are completed.\r\n<H3>Starts:</H3>		\r\n3 Minute Starting Sequence.\r\n<H3>Entry Fee:</H3>	\r\n$55/Boat (Includes Saturday night dinner).  A 10% ($5) discount will be given to all current members of US Sailing (proof is required at registration).  All competitors must be members of the Vanguard 15 Class Association.\r\n<H3>High Point Series:</H3>	\r\nHigh Point Series Regatta # 2 of 6.  Competitors must be current members of the SF Bay Vanguard 15 Fleet Association to score.\r\n<H3>Boats:</H3>\r\nA limited amount of boats are available for borrowing and charter on a first-come first-served basis.  Contact Shawn if you are interested.\r\n<H3>Regatta Documents:</H3>\r\n<A HREF=\"http://www.vanguard15.org/pdf/FR_PCC_NOR.pdf\">2000 PCC Notice of Race (.pdf)</A><BR>\r\n<A HREF=\"http://www.vanguard15.org/pdf/FR_PCC_SI.pdf\">2000 PCC Sailing Instructions (.pdf)</A><BR>\r\n<A HREF=\"http://www.vanguard15.org/pdf/FR_PCC_EF.pdf\">2000 PCC Entry Form (.pdf)</A><BR>\r\n<H3>Contact:</H3>	\r\nShawn Bennett<BR>     \r\nPhone:&nbsp;&nbsp;(510)649-9646<BR>	\r\nEmail:&nbsp;&nbsp;<A HREF=\"MAILTO:sbennett@etransport.com\">sbennett@etransport.com</A>\r\n</body></html>',NULL);
