INSERT INTO txt VALUES (75,'Tuesday was a perfect night for the 3rd tuesday night team race\npractice, there was a nice warm 5-10 knot breeze. We started out\ndoing some pig in the middle practice with 3 boats, then switched to\n2 on 2 around the leeward mark when one more boat joined us, last\nplace loses in this situation so we were constantly trying to spring\nthe boat in last until we finished. After we did a race of 2 on 2 we\nhad another boat join us so we did 2 on 3 with an imaginary 1 around\nthe leeward mark. We split it up to a 4,5,imaginary 1 verse a 2,3,6.\nThis made for some good team racing so we had about 4 leeward mark\nroundings sailing a digital N trying to switch it up every once it a\nwhile. We stopped racing around 8:30, had a couple beers and talked\nabout the racing. Good fun was had by all. We\'ll be getting 6 bow\nbumpers in two weeks to keep damage to a minimum, if anyone wants you\nwe might be able to add some on the order, we also have two that need\nto be paid for. Hope to see more out next time. \n\nHolt ');
