INSERT INTO txt VALUES (139,'How awesome would it be if we had 25 out on the line for the first\nThursday night of the 2005 season? \r\n\r\nAnd what would it take to drive that level of participation? \r\n\r\nHmmmm time for some marketing bullet points designed to have you\nheading off to the website to sign up! www.vanguard15.net \r\n\r\n1) The night is a celebration of Betsy Clevelands Birthday! Shes\nturning 26 or some other horrifyingly young age. \n\n2) Our post race bash is at La Barca! If that was a surprise to\nanyone, I have a bridge to sell you. \n\n3) Rumor has it that Avery Patton will be returning from Tahoe to\nlead the conga-line and dance on a table (with a strangely feline\nagility) in honor of her pal and mine whos off at business school. \n\n4) Betsy has challenged all comers to a body shot competition, but to\nenter, you have to have raced on the cove earlier in the evening. \n\n5) Madhavan has promised to write the post racing report, so youll\nhave better humor to ease the hang over on Friday Morning \n\nSo in addition to these fine incentives I promise NOT to spam the\nfleet with an email a day between now and then, as long as 25 real\nboats are signed up by next Thursday. Dont challenge me on this one\nIll enjoy writing them way more than youll enjoy reading them! \r\n\r\nIf you dont have a boat or a skipper sign up anyhow as looking to\nrace Well find a way to get you out there. \r\n\r\nWhat are you waiting for? Sign up now! ');
