INSERT INTO txt VALUES (216,'Another Scrambled Eggs Tues night Team Race... no set teams / no set\ncrews rotation. This is your chance to team race with the fleet\'s\nbest, learn a ton, and figure out who you might want to team up with\nfor this year\'s set-team regattas. \r\n\r\nPlease sign up individually: 1) Post your name in the \"Name\" box; 2)\nPost your sail # (if you have a boat you can use) or the next\navailable single-digit number (if you do not have a boat) in the\n\"Sail Number\" box; and 3)click \"Racing\". ');
INSERT INTO txt VALUES (217,'Greetings Vanguardians, \n\nBy popular demand, Mount Gay Rum returns to Thursday Night V15 racing\nfor the first time in..., well, since the last time I was social\nchair! I know you all love Mount Gay, so take the time to sign up\nsoon so I know how many bottles to purchase. The official \"Cup Nazi\"\n(yours truly) will only give out cups to those that are on the sign\nup list so make sure you sign up before noon on Thursday when I make\nthe BevMo run. \r\n\r\nIf you are thinking \"Wow, this is going to be awesome!\", well, you\nare right and I\'m not done yet! I\'m even going to bust out the BBQ\nand supply hot dogs, hamburgers, and chips for all that chose to\nsocialize after the racing. Cocktails, beers, soft drinks for our\nunderage competitiors, food for all, CAN WE BREAK THE ALL TIME\nCOMPETITOR RECORD??!! I sure as hell hope so! Sign up at:\nhttp://www.vanguard15.org/schedule/?r=252 \r\n\r\nRacing starts at 6:30pm sharp so don\'t be late. If you can\'t sail but\nwant to come down and join the festivities, Shannon can sure use some\nhelp with RC and you get the best seat in the house to watch the\naction. Hope to see you all there!! \r\n\r\n-Nick\r\n\r\nP.S. As all of you are aware by now, I am old and washed up in terms\nof the post race bar scene so I don\'t have a plan for you young,\nsingle, and motivated types. Bring some warm fuzzy gear and hang out\na little later at \"Club TI\"! ');
