INSERT INTO txt VALUES (354,'The Thursday Night Season begins in 18 days...April 6. Please\nremember to sign up on-line at www.vanguard15.org if you think you\nmight race. Alex Mountjoy has kindly agreed to be the first social\nchair of the season. He will only buy enough beer for those who sign\nup by Thursday morning! \r\n\r\nThis year, I will be assigning social chairs to a given Thursday\nnight. It will be your responsibility to find a substitute if you\ncannot make it. In order to be fair, I will honor any date requests\nif submitted before April 6. \r\n\r\nPlease bring $100 for Thursday Night fees and $25 for 2006 Fleet dues\nto the first Thursday Night you sail. Boats who do not pay will not\nhave their scores posted on-line. \r\n\r\nThere will be a Registration Form all skippers must fill out. You\nwill need to declare yourself a Varsity or Junior Varsity sailor.\nCollegiate skippers are expected to declare themselves Varsity. This\ndesignation only applies to the final awards, presented at the annual\nHoliday Classic in December. \r\n\r\nSailors will also need to fill out a TISC Medical & Liability Form if\nyou did not sail in 2005. Please, remember to have new crew fill out\nthis form when they sail. \r\n\r\nEach week, boats will be required to SIGN IN. If you do not sign in,\nyour scores will not be posted on-line. \r\n\r\nVanguard sailors...if you get a new sail, please put your complete\nsail number on the main. Last year, the number 8 became very popular\nbut it is very difficult for RC to score boats with the same number. \r\n\r\nBoth Lasers and V15s will be racing on Thursday Nights. Last year, we\nadded the restricted line to better manage starts & finishes. This\nyear, we will try to have an unrestricted line as long as it is\nmanageable. \r\n\r\nWe are still looking for reliable Race Committee. If you know of\nsomeone who could use $50 cash for approx. 4 hours work and free beer\nafter racing, given them my email or phone number. We now have a\nshort application form, that I can send them. \r\n\r\nLooking forward to seeing you on the water, \n\nCatherine King \n\nThursday Night Series Co-Chair \n\n(916) 752-5802 ');
