INSERT INTO txt VALUES (403,'Here is a recent note from the Laser Class Chairman. Any help is\ngreatly appreciated and will gladly be reciprocated at a Vanguard 15\nregatta in the future. \r\n\r\nHi, \n\nThe Elvstrom-Zellerbach Regatta, the BIG Dinghy Regatta on the City \n\nFront each year, is rapidly approaching and will be held this weekend\nof \n\nMay 6-7, 2006. It would be impossible to do justice to the incredible \n\nhistory of the two events which have been merged together to form\nthis \n\nregatta: The Zellerbach Regatta (dating from the early 60\'s!) for the \n\nFinn Class and The Elvstrom Regatta (dating from 1975 with Paul\nElvstrom \n\nhimself sailing the first event!) for Lasers. But you can get a\nflavor \n\njust by reading over the list of past winners - a veritable who\'s who\nof \n\nthe top names in sailing! \n\nThe tradition continues this year with 8 races planned over two days\nfor \n\nsix fleets: 49\'ers, 29\'ers, Finns, Lasers, Radials and Formula\nBoards. \n\nThis should be great action, certainly I know that the Lasers and \n\nRadials will turn out good fleets, and it should be great fun, \n\nespecially with that front row seat you get on a race committee boat! \n\nPlease let me know if you can help us out, either one day or both, on \n\nthe weekend of May 6-7. It is going to be great racing action and\nwill \n\nbe loads of fun to be part of! \n\nThanks! \r\n\r\nTracy Usher ');
