INSERT INTO txt VALUES (434,'\r\n:: Does anyone know of a masthead float that will work well\r\n:: on a V15? \r\n:: \r\n:: Please advise. \r\n\r\nAfter following through with more research I found a \"Baby Bob\"\nmasthead float made for a Hoby Cat H14 or H16 that works perfectly\nwith the mast on the V15. It bolts on in the exact two clevis pin\nholes on the top of the Vanguard mast. I\'m the first to admit it\nlooks a little unconventional on the top of a sleek V15 but it gives\nme and my kids a lot more peace of mind when the wind starts picking\nup and that a simple capsize is easily handled rather than the\ncomplications of a full turtle. It can be easily taken off when\nneeded. Now I just need to get some Vanguard decals to cover up the\nHobie Cat logo on the float! ');
